      <div class="msgContentFrame">I think he's talking about Class Quests, not Guildleves that give guild marks.  To answer the question, I'm not sure.  Story Quests can be done at 1, 10, and 20 Phys. Level.  I'm thinking Class Quests will follow a similar pattern, except starting at Rank 20.  This is only guesswork though.  The ZAM database, however, does have some quests listed under certain classes, but I'm not sure if they refer to the aforementioned Guildleves or to the Class Quests themselves.  We'll find out soon, I'm sure, when people start hitting Rank 20. </div>
